          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Two Motion Parameters </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">(for each Motion-Derivative) :</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End (motion-value) of Previous Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start (motion-value) of the Selected-Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The two motion parameter have two possible states: </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Read-Only </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">and </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Read-Write</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The state of each is determined by the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion-Derivative</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Control-Buttons,</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Laws" styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion-Law</link></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
