                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Match Control-Button</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">- two(2) States - </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">FORCE</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Start (motion-value) of the Selected-Segment = </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">or</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> ≠ End (motion-value) of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">Previous</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets" translate="true">?</text></para>
