    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Example: Blend-Point Editor: Three(3) Control-Buttons, EACH Motion-Derivative</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="AStandard" rowcount="2" colcount="1" style="width:100%;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:12px left ;"><image src="BPE-YaxisValues.ipp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">IN THE </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">BLEND-POINT EDITOR</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> (see image above), the </text><text styleclass="Separator-Header" translate="true">Y-axis values </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> for </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">motion-derivative</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> only are:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">End Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">(motion-value)</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true"> = 40mm</text></para>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">3 Control-Buttons</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> - see below</text></para>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Start Position </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">(</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">motion-value) </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">= 60mm</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">There are 8 different possible settings of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Control-Buttons. </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Blend-Point-Editor-Control_Buttons" styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">Control Buttons: States and Patterns</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-IT"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">In this example, the states of the </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">3 </text><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Control-Buttons</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> for </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> are:</text></para>
